      <title>Platinum 计划在 Aventiv 最新再融资举措中延长债务期限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/platinum-proposes-debt-extension-for-prison-phone-firm-aventiv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个月来，汤姆·戈尔斯 (Tom Gores) 的 Platinum Equity 一直在断断续续地进行谈判，以解决其陷入困境的监狱电话公司明年必须偿还的超过 10 亿美元的债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/platinum-proposes-debt-extension-for-prison-phone-firm-aventiv</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 17:29:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
